The paper deals with the combination of formalisms from knowledge representation, database theory, and process management to model enterprise systems. It also discusses formal verification techniques to ensure system correctness. These topics are closely related to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Databases (cs.DB), Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Programming Languages (cs.PL).
